」，加入獨創拔絲效果，將拉絲效果創新地融入傳統蓮蓉月，無需在食用前加熱，便能夠拉出一條條幼滑的鹹蛋黃絲，更可以在室温及保質期內保持拔絲效果。<br />\n<br />\n「拔絲蓮蓉月餅」以全新啡色長方形禮盒，配上細緻的金色絲線，勾劃出蓮花圖案。包裝瑰麗中帶出現代感，質感與觀感更具層次，極盡矜貴。一盒包含四個美味的「拔絲蓮蓉月餅」，適合與摯愛親友同享或送禮，讓今個中秋一起享受全新的中秋之味。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:51:20.000Z","msg":"到底加左幾多化學成份先做到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3941cde11c0a19d2b849184c7f2536e6b686d511","tid":2201281,"uid":312758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"434d5bef76dcc9228efaa5d79cb0461ba6046e8e","tid":2201281,"uid":225931,"like":13,"dislike":86,"score":-73,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T16:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:54:38.000Z","msg":"AA膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7ebfbafd0472b3cdf6cc9756b0f2931674a2a0","tid":2201281,"uid":245568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"434d5bef76dcc9228efaa5d79cb0461ba6046e8e","tid":2201281,"uid":225931,"like":13,"dislike":86,"score":-73,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T16:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:55:47.000Z","msg":"拉絲耳屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba703e5e1103588ba059aea690ecd8bd86d3453","tid":2201281,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62f2e66b08008cd6070e195d050071c93883795e","tid":2201281,"uid":27210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T16:36:59.000Z","msg":"唔好話<br />\n大把傻閪呢啲gimmick野仆去買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T18:02:24.000Z","msg":"蚑那狗呀嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50634612427c731ff2c9fd5dc359c381407f6533","tid":2201281,"uid":64072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d1e41b0363d34169f5c5420